<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=1440">
    <title>BABATHE.COM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/babathe.css">
    <script src="../../js/library.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header></header>
    <section class="container"> 
        <div class="login-wrap">
            <div>
                <div class="form-area w-half">
                    <h2 class="page-title">비회원 주문 조회<span class="font-s20">비회원으로 주문하신 내역을 조회하시려면<br>주문자명과 주문번호를 입력해 주세요.</span></h2>                    
                    <div class="form-wrap">
                        <div class="form-row">
                            <div class="form-box">
                                <input type="text" value=""  id="login2-1" placeholder="주문자명 입력"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-row">
                            <div class="form-box">
                                <input type="text" value=""  id="login2-2" placeholder="주문번호 입력"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="form-msg c-black">주문번호는 주문완료 후 발송된 이메일에서 확인하실 수 있습니다.</p>
                        <div class="btn-area">
                            <a href="#" class="btn primary w-full">비회원 주문 조회</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-half">
                    <div style="background:rgba(222,222,222,.3); width:340px; height:495px; margin-top:65px; text-align:center;">회원혜택 영역</div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn primary w-full">회원가입</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>